      "instruction": "<p>Before you start cooking, take your <strong>chicken </strong>out of the fridge, open the packet and let it air</p><p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Peel and finely chop your <strong>brown onion[s]</strong></p><p>Top, tail, peel and grate your <strong>carrot[s]</strong></p>",
