    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cover your <strong>free range chicken breast portion[s]</strong> in <strong>cling film</strong> and bash with a <strong>rolling pin</strong> until flattened to approx. 1cm thickness</p><p>Add a handful of <strong>flour </strong>to a plate, a splash of <strong>milk </strong>to a shallow bowl and your <strong>panko breadcrumbs</strong> to a separate plate</p><p>Coat the <strong>flattened chicken</strong> in the <strong>flour</strong>, tap off any excess, then add to the <strong>milk </strong>and firmly press into the <strong>breadcrumbs</strong> to evenly coat all over</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
