    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a pot with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>onion </strong>and <strong>half </strong>the<strong> grated carrot </strong>(save the rest for later!) and cook for 3 min or until beginning to soften</p><p>Once softened, add your <strong>curry powder </strong>with your <strong>ginger & garlic paste</strong> and 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>flour </strong>and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-copy-17-1693842511344-x200.jpg",
