          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-copy-16-1693842514297-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> breaded chicken</strong> and cook for 5-6 min on each side, pressing down firmly with a spatula until the outside is golden and the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>crispy chicken</strong></p><p>Tip: Cooking for 5? You may need to do this in batches!</p><p>Once done, transfer the <strong>crispy chicken</strong> to a clean board and slice into strips</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-copy-15-1693842517659-x200.jpg",
